# 使用 ggplot2 包进行作图

ggplot(china) + 
  geom_point(aes(x = year, y = lifeExp)) +
  geom_line(aes(x = year, y = lifeExp))

ggplot(china, aes(x = year, y = lifeExp)) + 
  geom_point() +
  geom_line()

#####

ggplot(gapminder, aes(x = year, y = lifeExp, group = country, color = continent)) +
  geom_line(size = 1.5, alpha = 0.5)

######

ggplot(gapminder) +
  geom_boxplot(aes(y = lifeExp, fill = continent))

# 使用 lm 进行线性回归

# 加载 broom 包，用来整理回归分析结果: tidy, glance, augment

model <- lm(lifeExp ~ year, gapminder)

#tidy 给出的是回归分析的系数
tidy(model)
## # A tibble: 2 x 5
##   term        estimate std.error statistic  p.value
##   <chr>          <dbl>     <dbl>     <dbl>    <dbl>
## 1 (Intercept) -586.      32.3        -18.1 2.90e-67
## 2 year           0.326    0.0163      20.0 7.55e-80
#glance 给出的是对模型的评价指标
glance(model)
## # A tibble: 1 x 11
##   r.squared adj.r.squared sigma statistic  p.value    df logLik    AIC

## # … with 3 more variables: BIC <dbl>, deviance <dbl>, df.residual <int>
#augment 给出的是模型的预测值

# mutate 创建新变量


gapminder %>% 
  nest(-country) %>%
  mutate(
    model = data %>% map(~lm(lifeExp~year, .)),
    tidy = model %>% map(tidy)
  ) %>% 
  unnest(tidy) %>% 
  filter(term == "year", p.value < 0.05, estimate > 0) %>% 
  arrange(-estimate)
